description:
As a coffee buyer 
 I want a basic machine that 
 I can put 10 kr coin in
 And get a black cup of coffee back.

steps.name: that the machine is plugged in
that the machine has ground coffee
the user inserts a 10 kr coin
the user receives a cup of coffee.
